Package ch.pschatzmann.edgar.reporting

Class AbstractModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.pschatzmann.edgar.reporting.AbstractModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EdgarModel
    public abstract class AbstractModel
extends java.lang.Object
    We can define the row fields, column fields and the value field. In addition we represent the database tables and their join relationships. This information is used to generate the SQL select command
    Author:
    pschatzmann
